Item.Name: Parts & accessories of motor vehicles, nes
Item.Description: Miscellaneous parts and accessories, for tractors, motor vehicles for the transport of ten or more persons, motor cars and other motor vehicles principally designed for the transport of persons, motor vehicles for the transport of goods and special purpose motor vehicles

Item.Name: Telephone sets & other voice/image transmission apparatus
Item.Description: Apparatus for the transmission or reception of voice, images or other data, incl. apparatus for communication in a wired or wireless network [such as a local or wide area network] (excluding line telephone sets with cordless handsets and transmission or reception apparatus of heading 8443, 8525, 8527 or 8528); transmission apparatus for radio-broadcasting or television

Item.Name: Parts & accessories of motor vehicle bodies
Item.Description: Parts and accessories of bodies for tractors, motor vehicles for the transport of ten or more persons, motor cars and other motor vehicles principally designed for the transport of persons, motor vehicles for the transport of goods and special purpose motor vehicles (excluding bumpers and parts thereof and safety seat belts)

Item.Name: Parts of refrigerating or freezing equipment
Item.Description: Parts of refrigerating or freezing equipment and heat pumps, n.e.s.

Item.Name: Laminated safety glass for vehicles
Item.Description: Laminated safety glass, of size and shape suitable for incorporation in motor vehicles, aircraft, spacecraft, vessels and other vehicles (excluding multiple-walled insulating units of glass)
